all scripts should be run from project directory

NaturalDocs-1.52/Config/Languages has been modified to support CoffeeScript:
Language: CoffeeScript

   Extension: coffee
   Line Comment: #
   Block Comment: ### ###
   Package Separator: .
   Function Prototype Enders: -> \n
   Variable Prototype Ender: \n

Topics has been modified to make a "trait" topic:
Topic Type: Trait

   Plural: Traits
   Scope: Start
   Class Hierarchy: Yes
   Page Title If First: Yes
   Can Group With: Classes, Interfaces

   Keywords:
      trait, traits
